                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151206-70-off386 t18151206-70-cd387"></join>, twenty-eight pounds weight of soap, value 1l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18151206-70-victim692" type="victimName">
                     Joseph 
                     Fletcher
                  <interp inst="t18151206-70-victim692" type="surname" value="Fletcher"></interp>
